{"tid":2360884,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"38歲深田恭子出嫁無了期 富貴男友三度結婚前疑轉軚","createTime":"2021-01-10T07:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T03:09:47.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7551d0ae136f78de5f7300f9303d74e3a6e11e3c","tid":2360884,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3fs5v-8HDYN9aG3ugvFV-e2pBG0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VYUVBTWOWVGYVPBF74P5Z2RMW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3fs5v-8HDYN9aG3ugvFV-e2pBG0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVYUVBTWOWVGYVPBF74P5Z2RMW4.jpg&h=48e33d6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本著名女星深田恭子早前度過38歲生日，一直盛傳她本於去年嫁入豪門，可惜受種種原因影響，令婚期一改再改，暫時無法榮升「老闆娘」。<br />\n<br />\n深田恭子早已超過適婚年紀，她撻着43歲富貴男友杉本宏之逾兩年，去年曾有報道指，恭子與杉本原定半年前搞婚禮，當時武漢肺炎疫情於當地越趨嚴重，恭子早已接下的工作均要延期，怎料婚期一改便到2021年。今日《女性自身》報道，深田恭子雖有機會是繼石原聰美、戶田惠梨香之後，下一位宣佈結婚的一線女星，但其男友杉本宏之最近向身邊朋友透露，要等公司上市後才會結婚，現時疫情在日本未受控制，故生意難免受到影響，使恭子出嫁計劃再遇暗湧。<br />\n<br />\n杉本宏之的公司是經營樓宇買賣、管理等，網民對他與深田恭子的婚事不大睇好，除質疑結婚跟上市有何關係外，有人更指男方疑似找藉口，替迫近40歲的恭子心急及擔憂。事關杉本宏之曾被爆是個大滾友，更曾兩度離婚，第二任太太是韓國女星吳世貞，據知離婚原因是杉本不忠所致。其實去年有報道指，恭子與杉本已簽下婚前協議，若日後離婚，女方不會分得丈夫任何財產， 除非其中一方不忠卻要付上賠償金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ifDvckgwwYYjHjw75kMhbYSgKMM=/802x796/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XD55P3YOSJAOXIKEBCJU7GCVGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FifDvckgwwYYjHjw75kMhbYSgKMM%3D%2F802x796%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXD55P3YOSJAOXIKEBCJU7GCVGY.jpg&h=a174dacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XKFDdZlAswQv3hBxooFqz_9X9UI=/802x522/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GND4NVCM4VCAPK4OJMMQUONZ7I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXKFDdZlAswQv3hBxooFqz_9X9UI%3D%2F802x522%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGND4NVCM4VCAPK4OJMMQUONZ7I.jpg&h=4de4a71a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5g-O3237lD-HAchtQ-hZqzx97DA=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ISG24GFAFNGDZCRYOG5LQS6LSI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5g-O3237lD-HAchtQ-hZqzx97DA%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FISG24GFAFNGDZCRYOG5LQS6LSI.jpg&h=ca7e6a9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a909eb20f6162c8baf928c6e7b10c25e5f1c3f7c","tid":2360884,"uid":75390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:33:01.000Z","msg":"想同佢結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc44cd63975bc249667db29bb22d91aecb4ddd9e","tid":2360884,"uid":261849,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"出來拍Av啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢真係好大隻又肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5c2f6170b6e58b5a517ed38e041acd18b4d14c","tid":2360884,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a909eb20f6162c8baf928c6e7b10c25e5f1c3f7c","tid":2360884,"uid":75390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:33:01.000Z","msg":"想同佢結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face